2. Work of Data Scientist
  ðŸ‘‰Understand the problem
  ðŸ‘‰Collect enough data (Files, Database, API & web scraping)
  ðŸ‘‰API[Programming Interface] (Google - Maps - User), Web Scrapping (means extract data from web.)
