  ðŸ‘‰Explore and visualize data
  ðŸ‘‰Analyse data using ML
  ðŸ‘‰Communicate the result

3. Data Science & Machine Learning (ML)
  ðŸ‘‰Machine Learning make our machine capable of learning by their own. ie. without being explicitly programmed.

  ðŸ‘‰Artificial Intelligence (or AI)
    Artificial Intelligence tries to make computers intelligent in order to minic the cognitive functions of humans. So it is a general field with a broad scope including: Computer Vision, Language Processing, Creativity, and Summarization.

  ðŸ‘‰Machine Learning (or ML)
    Machine Learning is the branch of AI that covers the statistical part of Artificial Intelligence, which teaches the computer to solve problems by looking at hundreds or thousands of examples, learning from them, and then using that experience to solve the same problem in new situations.

  ðŸ‘‰Deep Learning (or DL)
    Deep Learning is a very special field of Machine Learning where computers can actually learn and make intelligent decisions on their own. It involves a deeper level of automation in comparison with most machine learning algorithms.

